name: Akkss Foundation
briefDescription: Akkss foundation is a registered trust that deals in the education and health sector. We do run a school with 60 kids and a public library. We are currently having 4000 books in the library and in school, we do teach students at a very minimal cost of 5Rs per day also we do provide them stationary, uniform, course and all other resources. We also organise blood donation camp, planting drives etc.
